00:22:20.835 --> 00:22:23.140
It could be some speculator.

00:22:23.140 --> 00:22:24.470
You don't have to go
to the farmer.

00:22:24.470 --> 00:22:27.780
You can go to somebody else and
say, I'd like to buy an

00:22:27.780 --> 00:22:30.230
