over there.

00:22:30.230 --> 00:22:32.810
And someone would say, sure,
I'll sell you an option on it.

00:22:32.810 --> 00:22:33.640
And then I'm good for it.

00:22:33.640 --> 00:22:36.070
That means I have to go and buy
it at whatever price from

00:22:36.070 --> 00:22:36.870
the farmer.

00:22:36.870 --> 00:22:38.450
