the Great Depression.

01:05:41.350 --> 01:05:45.260
1929 precedes it, it's
somewhere in here.

01:05:45.260 --> 01:05:49.710
But somehow people got really
rattled by the 1929 stock

01:05:49.710 --> 01:05:51.590
