01:05:51.590 --> 01:05:54.930
And not just in the U.S. This is
U.S. data, but you'll find

01:05:54.930 --> 01:05:57.080
this all over the world.

01:05:57.080 --> 01:06:02.430
It led to a full decade of
tremendous stock market

01:06:02.430 --> 01:06:09.200
volatility around the world,
that has never

01:06:09.200 --> 01:06:11.850
been repeated since.

01:06:11.850 --> 01:06:17.640
The recent financial crisis
